    PersistenceManager, RemotePersistenceManager

    public class MCSStoragePersistenceManager
extends MCSPersistenceManager
    This class overwrites the standard entity CRUD methods that are called during data synchronization, and implements the methods by calling the MCS storage specific methods in the superclass. This allows us to manipulate MCS storage objets in offline mode and use the standard AMPA data synchronization mechanism later when we are online again.
